phylo3D.parser.nexus
Class TreeBlockParser

java.lang.Object
  phylo3D.parser.nexus.TreeBlockParser
public class TreeBlockParser
extends java.lang.Object

Parses the tree block in the NEXUS format as output by PAUP. Assumes that there is both a translate section and a tree definition in the tree section.

Author:
Tim Hughes (Computational Biology Unit - University of Bergen - Norway)
